                            <comment id="13958612" author="mduerig" created="Thu, 3 Apr 2014 08:09:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch looks good to me. +1 for applying if this gets you unblocked. However please &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jukkaz&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jukkaz&quot;&gt;jukkaz&lt;/a&gt; could you also have a look as you introduced the latest optimisations in this area so we don&apos;t overlook anything. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
